What,the,Microtransaction,API,does,in,addition,to,the,Transaction,API,is,to,propagate,smaller,and,more,frequent,transactions,that,still,exist,on,the,blockchain,and,are,still,publicly,auditable,BlockCypher,pays,the,mining,fees,for,the,first,microtransactions,After,that,number,the,company,optimizes,a,fee,to,gain,balance,and,achieve,results